We can use the following trick to compute $54 \times 46$ in our head:

\begin{align*}
54 \times 46 &= (50 + 4)(50 - 4)\\
&= 50^2 - 4^2\\
&= 2500 - 16\\
&= \boxed{2484}
\end{align*}
Final Answer: The final answer is 2484. I hope it is correct.

